subSections.title: Usage notes
subSections.text: The codepoint U+4CA4 once both represented ⿰魚酒 (traditional) and ⿰鱼酒 (simplified). Later, it is disunified for compatibility. Now ⿰魚酒 (traditional) belongs to U+9FD0.
